'''''Redbook'' (23 November 1967)''' is an issue of the magazine ''[[Wikipedia:Redbook|Redbook]]''. The issue includes [[J.R.R. Tolkien]]'s "[[Smith of Wootton Major]]", being the first publication of the short story in the United States.<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=http://www.tolkienbooks.net/php/details.php?reference=54100|articlename=Smith of Wootton Major. 1967|dated=|website=TB|accessed=1 September 2012}}</ref>
